Everyone else just exists in the world, as if they think its metal and have something stopping them from just reaching out and trying, trying to see if they can form it, or they just don't care to learn how. There's nothing I want more than to be like this certain kind of creator, but none of them want to be like anyone else but themselves. I wish I knew how.
